paytable.buy_bonus_desc:
Buy Bonus. A player can buy a bonus at the price pictured above the button. If the player increases the bet, the buy bonus price will be automatically increased. Spins start after buying the bonus. The next spin triggers a bonus game. 

Chance 2x feature. There is a possibility to buy the Chance x2 feature in the game. It increases the bet and gives the player more chances to play bonus games. The Chance x2 feature is disabled if the Buy Bonus feature is active.
paytable.free_spins:
Free Spins. 4 Scatter symbols hit anywhere on the screen award 10 Free Spins, 5 Scatters - 20 Free Spins, 6 Scatters - 30 Free Spins.  If 3 or more Scatters drop during the Bonus Round player gets 5 additional free spins.

Multiplier symbol. Whenever the symbol hits, it takes a random multiplier value from 2x to 100x. When the tumbling sequence ends, the value of all multiplier symbols on the screen are added together and the total win of the sequence is multiplied by the final value.
paytable.scatter_desc: Scatter pays on any position in the main game. During the Free Spins Round they only re-trigger Free Spins.
paytable.multiplier_desc: Multiplier symbol is present on the reels only during the Free Spins Round. Whenever the symbol hits it takes a random multiplier value from 2x to 100x.
paytable.buy_bonus_new_desc:
Buy Bonus. A player can instantly start a Free Spin game at the price pictured above the button. If the player increases the bet, the buy bonus price will be automatically increased. Spins start after buying the bonus. The next spin triggers a bonus game.

Chance x2 feature. There is a possibility to buy the Chance x2 feature in the game. It slightly increases the bet and gives a player more chances to play bonus games. The Chance x2 feature is disabled if the Buy Bonus feature is active.
paytable.free_spins_new_desc:
Free Spins. During the Bonus round if 3+ Scatter symbols drop on the reels player gets 5 additional Free Spins, if 4 Scatters - 10 Free Spins, 5 Scatters - 20 Free Spins, 6 Scatters - 30 Free Spins.

Multiplier symbol. Whenever the symbol hits it takes a random multiplier value from x2 to x100. When the tumbling sequence ends, the value of all multiplier symbols on the screen are added together and the total win of the sequence is multiplied by the final value.
paytable.scatter_new_desc: Scatter pays on any position in the main game.
paytable.multiplier_new_desc: Multiplier symbol is present on the reels only during the Free Spins Round. Whenever the symbol hits it takes a random multiplier value from x2 to x100.
